#: ../../content/guides/arguments.md:363
msgid ""
"See also [`RELENG_EXEC`](env-releng-exec) (environment) and [`releng_args"
"`](vars-releng_args) (configuration)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/arguments.md:367
msgid "`<pkg>-extract`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/arguments.md:369
msgid "Performs the extraction stage for the package."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/arguments.md:375
msgid ""
"On success, the specified package will have completed its extraction "
"stage. If the provided package name does not exist, a notification will "
"be generated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/arguments.md:379
msgid "See also the [`extract`](action-extract) action."
