msgid "`--profile [<profile>]`, `-P [<profile>]`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/arguments.md:802
msgid ""
"Configure a profile to run with. Providing this option is only applicable"
" if a project accepts custom profile options. Multiple profiles can be "
"provided by repeating this argument. Multiple profiles can also be "
"provided in a single argument where profiles are separated by a comma "
"(`,`) or a semicolon (`;`)."
